{"word":"G5350 - φθέγγομαι - phthéngomai - ftheng'-gom-ahee - Speak","slug":"G5350","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φθέγγομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>phthéngomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ftheng'-gom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Speak"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C6;&#x03B8;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03B3;&#x03B3;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - phtheggomai</b> - <i>ftheng'-gom-ahee</i><p/>Probably akin to <a href=\"#/G5338\">G5338</a> and thus to <a href=\"#/G5346\">G5346</a>; to <i>utter</i> a clear sound, that is, (genitive case) to <i>proclaim:</i> - speak."}]}